column5: it was a couple days OOS but it was hooked deep    you're welcome in advance Nick, for pumping up Team 6, yeah, I rock!
shouldn't you be watching the game, not mocking my reports?
shouldn't you be watching the game, not mocking my reports?  I can multi task!
a couple more drinks for me, and I'm going to jump in the truck and drive up to RRFN and give you a Marty McSorley
